.）等 6 家实体列入不可靠实体清单，并采取以下处理措施： 一、禁止上述企业从事与中国有关的进出口活动； 二、禁止上述企业在中国境内新增投资。 本公告未尽事宜，按《不可靠实体清单规定》执行。 本公告自 2025 年 4 月 10 日 12 时 01 分起实施。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8cf35a58adcd965e0c9242a3f498516c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "102 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1893379214817857630"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI6aG7o8ffiL1NEAMaCTExNDQxMjEwMSCuqdm/BjAAOJIHQAxyEzE4OTMzNzkyMTQ4MTc4NTc2MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1744250060.971175", "card_id": "Q_1891170538384253061", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "首版江苏省米其林指南即将在南京发布，这对南京及江苏餐饮业意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2025 年 4 月 9 日，首版《江苏省米其林指南》将在南京正式发布，南京由此成为继北京、上海等城市后，中国内地第七个拥有米其林榜单的目的地。这对南京及江苏餐饮业意味着什么？南京米其林，将花落谁家？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-98df74309840cfbc7ef5bebf48e3f427_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "100 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1891170538384253061"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI6aG7o8ffiL1NEAMaCTExNDMxNDg5NyCwl7m/BjAAOCNADXITMTg5MTE3MDUzODM4NDI1MzA2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1744250060.971705", "card_id": "Q_1888997397650199745", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "路易七世为啥不故意制造意外让埃莉诺身亡，这样阿基坦公国不就是自己的了?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-aedc21517e1301c5f2e6b5b29a823183_b.j